title: Wardell Gray - 1996 - Memorial FLAC
description:
Wardell Gray - 1996 - Memorial

Most of the tracks on both this and volume two were originally issued in prior Prestige two-fer packages. The majority of the cuts were short studio sessions, but two of the 20 are extended blowing sessions from 1950 which included Dexter Gordon, Clark Terry and Sonny Criss...Other participants to these solid sessions included Art Farmer, Hampton Hawes, Frank Morgan, Sonny Clark, Teddy Charles, Al Haig and others. Both volumes are lovely. (AllMusic)
